<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id77719521-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s410ggg–3"><num value="410ggg–3">§ 410ggg–3.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="id77719522-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s410ggg–3/a"><num value="a" class="bold">(a)</num><heading class="bold"> In general</heading><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I79" class="indent3 firstIndent-2" id="id77719523-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s410ggg–3/a/1"><num value="1" class="bold">(1)</num><heading class="bold"> Oral histories, preservation, and visitor services</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1">There are authorized to be appropriated such sums as may be necessary to conduct oral histories and to carry out the preservation, interpretation, education, and other essential visitor services provided for by this subchapter.</p>
</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I79" class="indent3 firstIndent-2" id="id77719524-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s410ggg–3/a/2"><num value="2" class="bold">(2)</num><heading class="bold"> Artifacts</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1">There are authorized to be appropriated $1,000,000 for the acquisition and curation of historical artifacts related to the park.</p>
</content>
</paragraph>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="id77719525-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s410ggg–3/b"><num value="b" class="bold">(b)</num><heading class="bold"> Property acquisition</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated such sums as are necessary to acquire the properties listed in <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s410ggg–1/e/2">section 410ggg–1(e)(2) of this title</ref>.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="id77719526-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s410ggg–3/c"><num value="c" class="bold">(c)</num><heading class="bold"> Limitation on use of funds for S.S. RED OAK VICTORY</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">None of the funds authorized to be appropriated by this section may be used for the operation, maintenance, or preservation of the vessel S.S. RED OAK VICTORY.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<sourceCredit id="id77719527-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/106/352/s5">Pub. L. 106–352, § 5</ref>, <date date="2000-10-24">Oct. 24, 2000</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/114/1372">114 Stat. 1372</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
